# Advancement 

## 20 October 2017
### Project Launcher
> Split teams in 2 sub-teams : 
  - Interface workers (Clément, Rabah, Ossama, Salim) 
    - The goal, it's to think about, the interface style and the interactions bewteen the interface and the game code
  - Code workers (Michel, Kheireddine, Hugo, Félix, Maxime)
